#	Communications Protocol Test Script
#	Mean Client and Server relationship
#	This script fails!

#	start up the client
PInit
TInit
PListen 1
TListen 600

#	read 40 bytes of random data
#	wait for 3 seconds before posting the read command
WAIT 1
WAIT 180
TReadDataSync 40
BEEP

#	close down the connection
TClose
PClose
BEEP
